text: Aglaia euryanthera is a species of plant in the family Meliaceae. It is found in Australia (Queensland), West Papua (Indonesia), and Papua New Guinea. ==References== euryanthera Category:Sapindales of Australia Category:Flora of Western New Guinea Category:Flora of Papua New Guinea Category:Near threatened flora of Australia Category:Near threatened biota of Queensland Category:Flora of Queensland Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
